": 0.91, "negativeValue": false, "negNote": null, "note": "Real trades of players closest to him by PRODUCTION (points rank among same-season peers), age, contract AND years of control \u2014 so a controlled scorer matches other controlled scorers, not rentals. The return is only what his old team got back FROM the team that landed him; \u201cpackage\u201d means he wasn't the only piece going out, so that return isn't his alone. For the genuinely elite \u2014 who almost never trade, so their only comps are distressed sales \u2014 we show a MODELED estimate of what a player his caliber would command instead."}, "salaryDump": null, "fairContract": {"available": true, "age": 24, "valueWar": 0.58, "rate": 4710846, "terms": [{"years": 2, "endAge": 26, "projectedWar": [0.59, 0.59], "fairAav": 3554399, "totalValue": 7108798}, {"years": 3, "endAge": 27, "projectedWar": [0.59, 0.59, 0.57], "fairAav": 3522993, "totalValue": 10568980}, {"years": 4, "endAge": 28, "projectedWar": [0.59, 0.59, 0.57, 0.54], "fairAav": 3471959, "totalValue": 13887837}, {"years": 5, "endAge": 29, "projectedWar": [0.59, 0.59, 0.57, 0.54, 0.5], "fairAav": 3403652, "totalValue": 17018260}, {"years": 6, "endAge": 30, "projectedWar": [0.59, 0.59, 0.57, 0.54, 0.5, 0.46], "fairAav": 3326708, "totalValue": 19960249}, {"years": 7, "endAge": 31, "projectedWar": [0.59, 0.59, 0.57, 0.54, 0.5, 0.46, 0.41], "fairAav": 3238099, "totalValue": 22666696}, {"years": 8, "endAge": 32, "projectedWar": [0.59, 0.59, 0.57, 0.54, 0.5, 0.46, 0.41, 0.36], "fairAav": 3142200, "totalValue": 25137601}], "note": "Fair AAV = average projected annual market value over the term (aging-curve WAR walk x $4.71M/WAR, each year floored at the league minimum). Longer terms average in decline years, so the fair AAV falls. Real deals carry a term/security premium this does not model -- it is the production-fair anchor, not a prediction of the signing."}, "contractProjection": {"seasonStart": 2026, "status": "UFA", "aavLow": 1105055, "aavMid"